---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Book a Free AI Audit | Auto-Mate"
  description="Book a free 45-minute AI audit with Auto-Mate. We will map your workflow, identify your biggest automation opportunities, and show you exactly what we would build."
  currentPage="/contact"
>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section style="background: var(--color-am-dark); padding: 80px 0 64px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-am-border);">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="eyebrow">Free AI Audit</div>
      <h1 class="section-heading" style="font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 3.2rem); max-width: 640px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
        45 minutes. No commitment. Real answers.
      </h1>
      <p class="section-subheading">
        We will look at your actual workflow, identify where you are losing time and revenue, and show you exactly what a custom automation system would look like for your business.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CONTACT LAYOUT -->
  <section class="section" style="background: var(--color-am-mid);">
    <div class="container">
      <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.4fr; gap: 64px; align-items: start;" class="contact-grid">

        <!-- Left: What to expect + contact info -->
        <div>
          <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 28px;">What happens on the call</h2>

          <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 24px; margin-bottom: 40px;">

            <div style="display: flex; gap: 16px; align-items: flex-start;">
              <div style="width: 36px; height: 36px; background: var(--color-am-blue-dim); border: 1px solid rgba(79, 142, 247, 0.2); border-radius: 8px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0; font-family: var(--font-display); font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-am-blue); font-size: 0.9rem;">1</div>
              <div>
                <p style="font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 4px;">We map your workflow</p>
                <p style="font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--color-am-muted); line-height: 1.7;">Walk us through a typical week. We ask specific questions about where your team spends time on repetitive tasks.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div style="display: flex; gap: 16px; align-items: flex-start;">
              <div style="width: 36px; height: 36px; background: var(--color-am-blue-dim); border: 1px solid rgba(79, 142, 247, 0.2); border-radius: 8px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0; font-family: var(--font-display); font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-am-blue); font-size: 0.9rem;">2</div>
              <div>
                <p style="font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 4px;">We identify the opportunities</p>
                <p style="font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--color-am-muted); line-height: 1.7;">We rank your automation opportunities by value and complexity, so you know exactly where to start for the fastest return.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div style="display: flex; gap: 16px; align-items: flex-start;">
              <div style="width: 36px; height: 36px; background: var(--color-am-blue-dim); border: 1px solid rgba(79, 142, 247, 0.2); border-radius: 8px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0; font-family: var(--font-display); font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-am-blue); font-size: 0.9rem;">3</div>
              <div>
                <p style="font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 4px;">We show you what we would build</p>
                <p style="font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--color-am-muted); line-height: 1.7;">You leave the call knowing exactly what a system would look like, what it would do, and what your investment would be. No surprises later.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

          </div>

          <hr class="divider" style="margin-bottom: 32px;" />

          <p style="font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--color-am-subtle); margin-bottom: 16px;">Or reach out directly</p>

          <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 14px;">
            <a href="mailto:kaden@auto-mate.business" style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; color: var(--color-am-muted); font-size: 0.9rem; transition: color 0.2s;" onmouseover="this.style.color='var(--color-am-text)'" onmouseout="this.style.color='var(--color-am-muted)'">
              <div class="icon-box" style="width: 36px; height: 36px; margin: 0; border-radius: 8px;">
                <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-am-blue)" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                  <path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"/><polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              kaden@auto-mate.business
            </a>
            <a href="tel:8014583118" style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; color: var(--color-am-muted); font-size: 0.9rem; transition: color 0.2s;" onmouseover="this.style.color='var(--color-am-text)'" onmouseout="this.style.color='var(--color-am-muted)'">
              <div class="icon-box" style="width: 36px; height: 36px; margin: 0; border-radius: 8px;">
                <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-am-blue)" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                  <path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07A19.5 19.5 0 0 1 4.69 12 19.79 19.79 0 0 1 1.61 3.37 2 2 0 0 1 3.59 1h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72c.127.96.361 1.903.7 2.81a2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L7.91 8.54a16 16 0 0 0 5.55 5.55l.92-.92a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45c.907.339 1.85.573 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 21 16.92z"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              (801) 458-3118
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Right: Contact form -->
        <div class="card" style="padding: 40px;">
          <h2 style="font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px;">Book your free audit</h2>
          <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--color-am-muted); margin-bottom: 32px;">Fill this out and we will follow up within one business day to schedule a time.</p>

          <form
            action="https://formspree.io/f/placeholder"
            method="POST"
            style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 20px;"
          >
            <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 16px;" class="form-row">
              <div>
                <label for="first-name" style="display: block; font-size: 0.82rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-am-muted); margin-bottom: 8px; letter-spacing: 0.03em;">First Name</label>
                <input
                  type="text"
                  id="first-name"
                  name="first_name"
                  required
                  placeholder="Jane"
                  style="
                    width: 100%;
                    background: var(--color-am-surface);
                    border: 1px solid var(--color-am-border);
                    border-radius: 8px;
                    padding: 12px 14px;
                    color: var(--color-am-text);
                    font-size: 0.9rem;
                    font-family: var(--font-body);
                    outline: none;
                    transition: border-color 0.2s;
                  "
                  onfocus="this.style.borderColor='var(--color-am-blue)'"
                  onblur="this.style.borderColor='var(--color-am-border)'"
                />
              </div>
              <div>
                <label for="last-name" style="display: block; font-size: 0.82rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-am-muted); margin-bottom: 8px; letter-spacing: 0.03em;">Last Name</label>
                <input
                  type="text"
                  id="last-name"
                  name="last_name"
                  required
                  placeholder="Smith"
                  style="
                    width: 100%;
                    background: var(--color-am-surface);
                    border: 1px solid var(--color-am-border);
                    border-radius: 8px;
                    padding: 12px 14px;
                    color: var(--color-am-text);
                    font-size: 0.9rem;
                    font-family: var(--font-body);
                    outline: none;
                    transition: border-color 0.2s;
                  "
                  onfocus="this.style.borderColor='var(--color-am-blue)'"
                  onblur="this.style.borderColor='var(--color-am-border)'"
                />
              </div>
            </div>

            <div>
              <label for="email" style="display: block; font-size: 0.82rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-am-muted); margin-bottom: 8px; letter-spacing: 0.03em;">Business Email</label>
              <input
                type="email"
                id="email"
                name="email"
                required
                placeholder="jane@yourbusiness.com"
                style="
                  width: 100%;
                  background: var(--color-am-surface);
                  border: 1px solid var(--color-am-border);
                  border-radius: 8px;
                  padding: 12px 14px;
                  color: var(--color-am-text);
                  font-size: 0.9rem;
                  font-family: var(--font-body);
                  outline: none;
                  transition: border-color 0.2s;
                "
                onfocus="this.style.borderColor='var(--color-am-blue)'"
                onblur="this.style.borderColor='var(--color-am-border)'"
              />
            </div>

            <div>
              <label for="phone" style="display: block; font-size: 0.82rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-am-muted); margin-bottom: 8px; letter-spacing: 0.03em;">Phone (optional)</label>
              <input
                type="tel"
                id="phone"
                name="phone"
                placeholder="(555) 000-0000"
                style="
                  width: 100%;
                  background: var(--color-am-surface);
                  border: 1px solid var(--color-am-border);
                  border-radius: 8px;
                  padding: 12px 14px;
                  color: var(--color-am-text);
                  font-size: 0.9rem;
                  font-family: var(--font-body);
                  outline: none;
                  transition: border-color 0.2s;
                "
                onfocus="this.style.borderColor='var(--color-am-blue)'"
                onblur="this.style.borderColor='var(--color-am-border)'"
              />
            </div>

            <div>
              <label for="business" style="display: block; font-size: 0.82rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-am-muted); margin-bottom: 8px; letter-spacing: 0.03em;">Business Name</label>
              <input
                type="text"
                id="business"
                name="business_name"
                required
                placeholder="Your Business LLC"
                style="
                  width: 100%;
                  background: var(--color-am-surface);
                  border: 1px solid var(--color-am-border);
                  border-radius: 8px;
                  padding: 12px 14px;
                  color: var(--color-am-text);
                  font-size: 0.9rem;
                  font-family: var(--font-body);
                  outline: none;
                  transition: border-color 0.2s;
                "
                onfocus="this.style.borderColor='var(--color-am-blue)'"
                onblur="this.style.borderColor='var(--color-am-border)'"
              />
            </div>

            <div>
              <label for="revenue" style="display: block; font-size: 0.82rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-am-muted); margin-bottom: 8px; letter-spacing: 0.03em;">Annual Revenue Range</label>
              <select
                id="revenue"
                name="revenue_range"
                style="
                  width: 100%;
                  background: var(--color-am-surface);
                  border: 1px solid var(--color-am-border);
                  border-radius: 8px;
                  padding: 12px 14px;
                  color: var(--color-am-muted);
                  font-size: 0.9rem;
                  font-family: var(--font-body);
                  outline: none;
                  cursor: pointer;
                  appearance: none;
                "
                onfocus="this.style.borderColor='var(--color-am-blue)'"
                onblur="this.style.borderColor='var(--color-am-border)'"
              >
                <option value="">Select a range...</option>
                <option value="under-500k">Under $500K</option>
                <option value="500k-1m">$500K - $1M</option>
                <option value="1m-3m">$1M - $3M</option>
                <option value="3m-5m">$3M - $5M</option>
                <option value="over-5m">Over $5M</option>
              </select>
            </div>

            <div>
              <label for="message" style="display: block; font-size: 0.82rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-am-muted); margin-bottom: 8px; letter-spacing: 0.03em;">What is eating the most time in your operation right now?</label>
              <textarea
                id="message"
                name="message"
                rows="4"
                placeholder="Describe the manual work, the bottlenecks, or the processes that are slowing you down..."
                style="
                  width: 100%;
                  background: var(--color-am-surface);
                  border: 1px solid var(--color-am-border);
                  border-radius: 8px;
                  padding: 12px 14px;
                  color: var(--color-am-text);
                  font-size: 0.9rem;
                  font-family: var(--font-body);
                  outline: none;
                  resize: vertical;
                  min-height: 100px;
                  transition: border-color 0.2s;
                "
                onfocus="this.style.borderColor='var(--color-am-blue)'"
                onblur="this.style.borderColor='var(--color-am-border)'"
              ></textarea>
            </div>

            <button type="submit" class="btn-primary" style="width: 100%; justify-content: center; font-size: 1rem; padding: 14px;">
              Request My Free Audit
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><path d="M3 8h10M9 4l4 4-4 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
            </button>

            <p style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--color-am-subtle); text-align: center; line-height: 1.6;">
              We will follow up within one business day. No spam, no sales pressure.
            </p>
          </form>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .contact-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr !important;
    }
    .form-row {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr !important;
    }
  }

  input::placeholder,
  textarea::placeholder {
    color: var(--color-am-subtle);
  }

  select option {
    background: var(--color-am-surface);
    color: var(--color-am-text);
  }
</style>
